
17 years before the time of this story is when when the dalek empire was fallen. The Doctor and his army of companions in which he went back into time to claim. They defeated the daleks and turned them all into humans. Though it was not fully successful. The hatred stayed but other feelings were added.2 years later the daleks move to a planet of their own. this planet goes by the name of Plorix. This planet is much like earth, but once a year it rains diamonds.
17 Years after the fall of the daleks a girl by the name of Crim was born. What made this girl dangerous. She came directly from the dalek royal family ,now not so royal, and had more hatred then the generic dalek. this Story starts on her 17th birthday.LET THE TALE COMMENCE!!!